Generic name: Phenylephrine HCl + CPM + Paracetamol Dosage: 500 mg tablet Use: For the relief of clogged nose, body aches, fever, other minor respiratory tract infections. Indication of use: Adults & children 12 yrs. old & above: Take 1 tablet every 6 hours, or as directed by the doctor.
Product is sold per blister pack
